{"tid":1031111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清光緒三十一年（1905年）長相比較漂亮的男孩子，靠着色相勾引客人， 出賣肉體！！","createTime":"2019-02-21T12:08:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T07:54:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":87,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"e666793b49460b168d1e4c43ce3d1d64a2a359bc","tid":1031111,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:08:29.000Z","msg":"清光緒三十一年（1905年）<br />\n在胡同相公窯子內「相公」「兔子」，<br />\n是長相比較漂亮的男孩子，靠着色相勾引客人，<br />\n出賣肉體。<br />\n據說當時明朝定都北京的時候開始，<br />\n對當官的是有要求的，不准嫖娼。<br />\n不准嫖娼，也沒說不準玩相公。<br />\n裏面幾乎全部是唱戲的男孩子，油頭粉面，<br />\n長得比較漂亮，眉眼也好看，行為舉止像女的。<br />\n那些有錢人就去捧場，弄一張桌子，點上燈，<br />\n再弄點酒菜，邊喝邊看，旁邊還有人伺候着，<br />\n然後就和那些唱戲的男人摟摟抱抱。<br />\n唱戲快結束了，就到外邊去開房間。<br />\n等到南方妓女到了八大胡同，<br />\n就把相公窯子的生意給頂了，漸漸地消失。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P1zH9Sk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP1zH9Sk.png&h=2589ba62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ec4cfe9d70ce75e32bfebb4954e190274a180aef","tid":1031111,"uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:09:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1183582359/posts/10218591417034985?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1183582359%2Fposts%2F10218591417034985%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=YG7PnvT15JjBub1A77CHD0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=a81fbcea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1183582359/posts/10218591417034985?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ec336aafb63dab117467c422bb1cfc0760ce2da6","tid":1031111,"uid":22675,"like":231,"dislike":1,"score":230,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:10:00.000Z","msg":"原來偽娘歷史咁悠久"},{"pid":"f08383eb5e88be45d747085c50751e91e3ca78ad","tid":1031111,"uid":64191,"like":79,"dislike":0,"score":79,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:11:54.000Z","msg":"果然係國粹，到今時今日依然有呢類人"},{"pid":"04216fbe1023f01c93fa89941252f27431af55a5","tid":1031111,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T12:13:22.000Z","msg":